project:
Controls:

-Press the Arrow Keys to move Fawna. 
-Press Up to jump and press again to double-jump-- holding the key will jump higher!
-Press Space while on a button to toggle it on and off.
-Press the Down key while standing near a box to pick it up, and press again to release the box.
-Press the R key to restart the current level if you get stuck or hurt by an enemy or obstacle.

Goal:

-Turn on all of the buttons in the level to stop the machine and complete the level-- there are 3 buttons in each level!
-Boxes can be picked up and dropped, and can be stood on or stacked to reach greater heights. Metal boxes can be placed down on pressure plates, while wooden boxes cannot.
-Avoid gas clouds, spiky sticks, and flame monsters. Restart the level by pressing R if you get hit by them, or wait a few seconds for the level to reload.
-Good luck saving the forest from the machines!
